{"tid":1808246,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台空軍黑鷹直升機空難　參謀總長等 8 人死亡　5 人生還","createTime":"2020-01-02T08:54:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T08:54:16.000Z","uid":226984,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c067facf8686f2bfd670fa39fa3b399b39083c82","tid":1808246,"uid":226984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T08:54:16.000Z","msg":"台灣中央社報道，空軍一架 UH-60M 黑鷹直升機今天上午在烏來山區發生迫降意外，空軍下午召開記者會證實，包括參謀總長沈一鳴等 8 人無生命跡象，軍聞社記者陳映竹等 5 人生還。<br />\n<br />\n國防部上午在松山基地指揮部召開臨時記者會，空軍司令雄厚基上將表示，發生這起飛安事件心情很沉重，全機共 13 人，扣除正駕駛、副駕駛及機工長，共有 10 人前往慰問行程，並在上午 7 時 54 分從松山起飛、8 時 7 分松山 105 度 / 16 浬處光點消失烏來山區，最後位置於桶後溪溪谷。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3/%E5%8F%B0%E7%A9%BA%E8%BB%8D%E9%BB%91%E9%B7%B9%E7%9B%B4%E5%8D%87%E6%A9%9F%E7%A9%BA%E9%9B%A3-%E5%8F%83%E8%AC%80%E7%B8%BD%E9%95%B7%E7%AD%89-8-%E4%BA%BA%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1-5-%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E9%82%84/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2F%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%2F%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E8%25BB%258D%25E9%25BB%2591%25E9%25B7%25B9%25E7%259B%25B4%25E5%258D%2587%25E6%25A9%259F%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E9%259B%25A3-%25E5%258F%2583%25E8%25AC%2580%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E9%2595%25B7%25E7%25AD%2589-8-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E4%25BA%25A1-5-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2594%259F%25E9%2582%2584%2F&d=lD%2FUaJpd7HswZ4lFnFCcPhUxn6Ez5IAhGrAWUjzTwv4%3D&h=4f34b0e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2F%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%2F%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E8%25BB%258D%25E9%25BB%2591%25E9%25B7%25B9%25E7%259B%25B4%25E5%258D%2587%25E6%25A9%259F%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E9%259B%25A3-%25E5%258F%2583%25E8%25AC%2580%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E9%2595%25B7%25E7%25AD%2589-8-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E4%25BA%25A1-5-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2594%259F%25E9%2582%2584%2F&h=ac577e59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3/%E5%8F%B0%E7%A9%BA%E8%BB%8D%E9%BB%91%E9%B7%B9%E7%9B%B4%E5%8